Wouldn't you?

25:36.378 --> 25:37.820
I would have thought two or three hundred.

25:38.681 --> 25:50.680
For example, one room that has been divided into two parts in the 18th century, so it has been changed a little at a later time.

25:50.720 --> 25:52.463
These are very spacious as well.

25:52.563 --> 25:53.365
That's right.

