Like the Archibaldau paintings also?

31:41.118 --> 31:43.162
Oh, we're going to see the Archibaldau paintings?

31:43.222 --> 31:44.425
Yes, I think it will be arranged.

31:44.445 --> 31:45.026
Oh, that's great.

31:46.829 --> 31:51.218
My book has the Archibaldau painting on the back, on the dust jacket, the librarian.

31:52.360 --> 31:57.150
It would really be great.

