32:29.465 --> 32:33.450
Was this a room for study, too, or mainly just for storage?

32:33.950 --> 32:38.896
No, only for storage, but there are odd desks, and there have been chairs all the time.

32:39.276 --> 32:42.600
We know that from the inventory that was made when he died.

32:43.641 --> 32:46.424
So he has been sitting here studying his books.

32:47.566 --> 32:51.130
Where we are right now, he ended up being here.

32:51.190 --> 32:54.974
Are any of these pieces of furniture contemporary?

32:54.994 --> 32:58.358
No, they are later, from the 18th century.

32:59.047 --> 32:59.628
Most of them.

