Here is an original chair, but the chair was not used for... Yes, original floor.

33:05.776 --> 33:10.262
But this chair was not used for studying.

33:11.023 --> 33:18.413
It's a chair for, we think, one of our kings who was quite easy as he was old.

33:19.575 --> 33:27.045
