38:33.385 --> 38:39.835
So today they're all placed by owner, but in the 1820s that was all mixed up.

38:40.696 --> 38:44.582
So that's also an important part of your catalogue you're doing now, is to trace it.

38:44.663 --> 38:45.324
Where did it come from?

38:45.344 --> 38:46.465
That's what you're doing.

38:46.505 --> 38:49.269
You're trying to determine... I think you should tell us that.

38:49.769 --> 38:54.856
We started... I wasn't here in 1967, but this work started in 1967.

38:56.318 --> 39:00.563
And all the libraries were mixed at that time.

39:00.984 --> 39:06.010
