What would you say is the great significance, in your view, of this library?

41:13.987 --> 41:18.373
What is the significance, other than the historical significance?

41:18.393 --> 41:23.620
Is there a significance in terms of the book itself?

41:23.680 --> 41:27.685
What would a scholar find of particular interest here in these books?

